{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":907,"text":"You know, it's a big privilege for me"},{"time":3335,"text":"to be working in one of the\nbiodiversity hotspots in the world:"},{"time":7227,"text":"the Mascarene Islands in the Indian Ocean."},{"time":9928,"text":"These islands — Mauritius,\nRodrigues, and Réunion —"},{"time":13673,"text":"along with the island of Madagascar,"},{"time":16811,"text":"they are blessed with unique plants"},{"time":18727,"text":"found nowhere else in the world."},{"time":20840,"text":"And today I will tell you \nabout five of them"},{"time":23529,"text":"and their particular features"},{"time":25524,"text":"and why these plants are so unique."}]},{"cues":[{"time":28408,"text":"Take a look at this plant."},{"time":29968,"text":"I call it benjoin in the local vernacular,"},{"time":33372,"text":"and the botanical name \nis Terminalia bentzoe,"},{"time":37298,"text":"subspecies bentzoe."},{"time":39199,"text":"This subspecies is endemic to Mauritius,"},{"time":42507,"text":"and its particular feature"},{"time":44318,"text":"is its heterophylly."},{"time":46792,"text":"What do I mean by heterophylly?"},{"time":48918,"text":"It's that the same plant"},{"time":50481,"text":"has got leaves that are different shapes and sizes."},{"time":53564,"text":"Now, these plants have evolved"},{"time":55149,"text":"very far away from the mainland,"},{"time":57503,"text":"and within specific ecosystems."},{"time":60901,"text":"Often, these particular features"},{"time":63725,"text":"have evolved as a response to the threat"},{"time":66536,"text":"presented by the local fauna,"},{"time":68973,"text":"in this case, grazing tortoises."},{"time":72593,"text":"Tortoises are known to have poor eyesight,"},{"time":75749,"text":"and as such, they tend to avoid the plants"},{"time":78235,"text":"they don't recognize."},{"time":80294,"text":"So this evolutionary \nfoil safeguards the plant"},{"time":83668,"text":"against these rather cute animals,"},{"time":86593,"text":"and protects it and of course \nensures its survival."}]},{"cues":[{"time":91651,"text":"Now the question you're \nprobably asking yourself is,"},{"time":94661,"text":"why is she telling us all these stories?"},{"time":97562,"text":"The reason for that is that we tend to overlook"},{"time":101248,"text":"the diversity and the variety of the natural world."},{"time":105632,"text":"These particular habitats are unique"},{"time":108525,"text":"and they are host to a whole lot of plants."},{"time":112753,"text":"We don't realize how valuable"},{"time":114924,"text":"and how precious these resources are,"},{"time":117534,"text":"and yet, through our insouciance,"},{"time":119729,"text":"we keep on destroying them."},{"time":121898,"text":"We're all familiar"},{"time":123630,"text":"with the macro impact of urbanization,"},{"time":126825,"text":"climate change, resource exploitation,"},{"time":130267,"text":"but when that one last plant —"},{"time":132440,"text":"or animal for that matter —"},{"time":134649,"text":"when that very last specimen"},{"time":136848,"text":"has disappeared from the face of this Earth,"},{"time":138959,"text":"we would have lost"},{"time":140355,"text":"an entire subset of the Earth's biology,"},{"time":144261,"text":"and with it, important plants \nwith medicinal potential"},{"time":147939,"text":"or which could have ingredients"},{"time":149874,"text":"that would speak to the cosmetic,"},{"time":151395,"text":"nutrition, pharma,"},{"time":153316,"text":"and even the ethno-veterinary sectors,"},{"time":155735,"text":"be gone forever."},{"time":157478,"text":"And here we have a very prime example"},{"time":159413,"text":"of the iconic dodo, which comes from Mauritius,"},{"time":162158,"text":"and, of course, we know is \nnow a symbol of extinction."}]},{"cues":[{"time":166545,"text":"We know plants have a \nfundamental role to play."},{"time":169165,"text":"Well, first of all, they feed us"},{"time":171000,"text":"and they also give us \nthe oxygen we breathe,"},{"time":173890,"text":"but plants are also the source"},{"time":176207,"text":"of important, biologically active ingredients"},{"time":179762,"text":"that we should be studying very carefully,"},{"time":182964,"text":"because human societies over the millennia,"},{"time":187254,"text":"they have developed important knowledge,"},{"time":190302,"text":"cultural traditions,"},{"time":192120,"text":"and important plant-based medicinal resources."},{"time":196416,"text":"Here's a data point:"},{"time":198401,"text":"1.4 percent of the entire land surface"},{"time":202563,"text":"is home to 40 percent of\nthe species of higher plants,"},{"time":206467,"text":"35 percent of the species of vertebrates,"},{"time":209155,"text":"and this 1.4 percent"},{"time":211698,"text":"represents the 25 biodiversity hotspots in the world,"},{"time":216366,"text":"and this 1.4 percent of the entire land surface"},{"time":219524,"text":"already provides for 35 percent"},{"time":222406,"text":"of the ecosystem services"},{"time":224240,"text":"that vulnerable people depend on."},{"time":226918,"text":"And as you can see,"},{"time":228266,"text":"the island of Mauritius"},{"time":229679,"text":"where I work and where I live,"},{"time":231762,"text":"belongs to one such biodiversity hotspot,"},{"time":234467,"text":"and I study the unique plants"},{"time":236681,"text":"on the island for their \nbiomedical applications."}]},{"cues":[{"time":240343,"text":"Now, let's go back again"},{"time":241680,"text":"to that first plant I showed you,"},{"time":243520,"text":"the one, of course, with \ndifferent-shaped leaves"},{"time":246547,"text":"and different sizes, Terminalia bentzoe,"},{"time":249403,"text":"subspecies bentzoe,"},{"time":251070,"text":"a plant only found in Mauritius."},{"time":253665,"text":"Now, the local people,"},{"time":255110,"text":"they used a decoction of the leaves"},{"time":257336,"text":"against infectious diseases."},{"time":259867,"text":"Now our work, that is,"},{"time":262319,"text":"the scientific validation of \nthis traditional information,"},{"time":265728,"text":"has shown that precisely"},{"time":267800,"text":"that leaf extract shows activity, potent activity,"},{"time":272129,"text":"against a wide range of bacteria"},{"time":274351,"text":"that could be pathogenic to humans."},{"time":277427,"text":"Now, could this plant be the answer"},{"time":279868,"text":"to antibiotic resistance?"},{"time":282489,"text":"You know, antibiotic resistance is proving to be"},{"time":284840,"text":"a big challenge globally."},{"time":287560,"text":"While we may not be sure, one thing is certain:"},{"time":290363,"text":"we will not want this plant to disappear."},{"time":292972,"text":"But the harsh reality is that"},{"time":295616,"text":"this particular plant is in fact"},{"time":297600,"text":"considered to be vulnerable"},{"time":299470,"text":"in its natural habitat."}]},{"cues":[{"time":301630,"text":"This brings me to another example."},{"time":303778,"text":"This bush here is known as baume de l'ile plate"},{"time":307568,"text":"in the local vernacular."},{"time":309290,"text":"The botanical name is Psiadia arguta."},{"time":311945,"text":"It's a plant which is rare,"},{"time":313836,"text":"which is endemic to Mauritius."},{"time":316548,"text":"It used to grow on the mainland,"},{"time":317770,"text":"but through the sheer \npressures of urbanization"},{"time":320213,"text":"has been pushed out of the mainland,"},{"time":322492,"text":"and we've managed to bring it back"},{"time":324193,"text":"from the brink of extinction"},{"time":325669,"text":"by developing in vitro plants"},{"time":327736,"text":"which are now growing in the wild."},{"time":329584,"text":"Now, one thing I must \npoint out straightaway"},{"time":331780,"text":"is that not all plants"},{"time":334657,"text":"can be developed in vitro."},{"time":337573,"text":"While we humans, we are \nhappy in our comfort zone,"},{"time":341396,"text":"these plants also need"},{"time":343632,"text":"their ecosystem to be preserved,"},{"time":346366,"text":"and they don't react — endemic plants"},{"time":348199,"text":"don't react to very harsh \nchanges in their ecosystem,"},{"time":351518,"text":"and yet we know what are the challenges"},{"time":353779,"text":"that climate change, for example,"},{"time":354867,"text":"is posing to these plants."},{"time":356910,"text":"Now, the local people again use the leaves"},{"time":359438,"text":"in traditional medicine"},{"time":361192,"text":"against respiratory problems."},{"time":363872,"text":"Now, our preliminary labwork"},{"time":365961,"text":"on the leaf extract has shown"},{"time":367693,"text":"that precisely these \nleaves contain ingredients"},{"time":371822,"text":"that are very close, \nin terms of structures,"},{"time":374917,"text":"chemical structures, to those medicines"},{"time":377283,"text":"which are sold in the chemist's shop"},{"time":378802,"text":"against asthma."},{"time":380777,"text":"So who knows"},{"time":382687,"text":"what humanity will benefit from"},{"time":384773,"text":"should this plant decide \nto reveal all its secrets."}]},{"cues":[{"time":390191,"text":"Now, I come from the developing world"},{"time":392682,"text":"where we are forever being \nchallenged with this issue"},{"time":395485,"text":"of population explosion."},{"time":397879,"text":"Africa is the continent \nwhich is getting younger,"},{"time":400693,"text":"and whenever one talks \nabout population explosion,"},{"time":404396,"text":"one talks about the issue of food security"},{"time":406901,"text":"as being the other side of the same coin."},{"time":409581,"text":"Now this plant here, the baobab,"},{"time":411899,"text":"could be part of the answer."},{"time":413421,"text":"It's an underutilized, neglected food plant."},{"time":416566,"text":"It defines the landscape of West Africa,"},{"time":419059,"text":"where it is known as the tree of life,"},{"time":421605,"text":"and later on I will tell you why"},{"time":424103,"text":"the Africans consider it to be the tree of life."},{"time":427214,"text":"Now interestingly, there are many legends"},{"time":429132,"text":"which are associated with this plant."},{"time":431240,"text":"Because of its sheer size,"},{"time":433012,"text":"it was meant to be lording over lesser plants,"},{"time":435914,"text":"so God didn't like this arrogance,"},{"time":437872,"text":"uprooted it, and planted it upside down,"},{"time":440660,"text":"hence its particular shape."},{"time":443182,"text":"And if you look at this tree again"},{"time":445690,"text":"within the African context,"},{"time":447852,"text":"in West Africa, it's known \nas the palaver tree,"},{"time":451517,"text":"because it performs great social functions."},{"time":454587,"text":"Now if you have a problem in the community,"},{"time":456806,"text":"meeting under the palaver tree"},{"time":458544,"text":"with the chiefs or the tribesmen"},{"time":460523,"text":"would be synonymous to trying to find a solution"},{"time":462685,"text":"to that particular problem,"},{"time":464130,"text":"and also to reinforce trust and respect"},{"time":467070,"text":"among members of the community."},{"time":469591,"text":"From the scientific point of view,"},{"time":471987,"text":"there are eight species of baobab in the world."},{"time":474682,"text":"There's one from Africa,"},{"time":476664,"text":"one from Australia,"},{"time":478333,"text":"and six are endemic"},{"time":481080,"text":"to the island of Madagascar."},{"time":482727,"text":"The one I have showed you"},{"time":484359,"text":"is the one from Africa,"},{"time":485949,"text":"Adansonia digitata."},{"time":487870,"text":"Now, the flower, this \nbeautiful white flower,"},{"time":490190,"text":"it opens at night, is pollinated by bats,"},{"time":492314,"text":"and it gives rise to the fruit"},{"time":494913,"text":"which is curiously known"},{"time":496465,"text":"as the monkey apple."},{"time":498200,"text":"The monkeys are not stupid animals."},{"time":499693,"text":"They know what's good for them."},{"time":501426,"text":"Now, if you open the fruit of the baobab,"},{"time":504227,"text":"you'll see a white, floury pulp,"},{"time":506820,"text":"which is very rich in nutrients"},{"time":508917,"text":"and has got protein,"},{"time":511291,"text":"more protein than in human milk."},{"time":515409,"text":"Yes, you heard right:"},{"time":517197,"text":"more protein than in human milk."},{"time":520605,"text":"And this is one of the reasons why"},{"time":522495,"text":"the nutrition companies of this world,"},{"time":524317,"text":"they are looking for this fruit to provide"},{"time":526702,"text":"what we know as reinforced food."},{"time":529289,"text":"The seeds give an oil, a very stable oil"},{"time":533170,"text":"which is sought after \nby the cosmetic industry"},{"time":536240,"text":"to give to produce body lotions, for example."},{"time":539502,"text":"And if you look at the trunk,"},{"time":541131,"text":"the trunk, of course, safeguards water,"},{"time":544734,"text":"which is often harvested by a thirsty traveler,"},{"time":547535,"text":"and the leaves are used in traditional medicine"},{"time":549213,"text":"against infectious disease."},{"time":551168,"text":"Now, you can see now why the Africans consider it"},{"time":553744,"text":"to be the tree of life."},{"time":555544,"text":"It's a complete plant,"},{"time":557209,"text":"and in fact, the sheer size of these trees"},{"time":559751,"text":"is hiding a massive potential,"},{"time":561854,"text":"not only for the pharma, nutrition,\nand the cosmetic industry."},{"time":565296,"text":"What I have showed you here"},{"time":567302,"text":"is only the species from Africa,"},{"time":569532,"text":"Adansonia digitata."},{"time":571416,"text":"We have six species yet in Madagascar,"},{"time":574080,"text":"and we don't know what \nis the potential of this plant,"},{"time":577564,"text":"but one thing we know is that the flora"},{"time":580030,"text":"is considered to be \nthreatened with extinction."}]},{"cues":[{"time":582592,"text":"Let me take you to Africa again,"},{"time":585796,"text":"and introduce you to one of my very favorite,"},{"time":588300,"text":"the resurrection plant."},{"time":590130,"text":"Now here you'll find"},{"time":591477,"text":"that even Jesus has competition."},{"time":593395,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":594998,"text":"Now, this plant here has developed"},{"time":597991,"text":"remarkable tolerance to drought,"},{"time":600970,"text":"which enables it to withstand"},{"time":603068,"text":"up to 98 percent dehydration \nover the period of a year"},{"time":607313,"text":"without damage,"},{"time":609417,"text":"and yet it can regenerate \nitself almost completely"},{"time":613567,"text":"overnight, over 24 hours, and flower."},{"time":617647,"text":"Now, us human beings,"},{"time":619880,"text":"we're always on the lookout for the elixir of youth."},{"time":623106,"text":"We don't want to get old, and rightly so."},{"time":624940,"text":"Why should we, especially if you can afford it?"},{"time":628179,"text":"And this gives you an indication"},{"time":630362,"text":"of what the plant looks like before."},{"time":633164,"text":"Now, if you are an inexperienced gardener,"},{"time":636020,"text":"the first thing you'll do \nwhen you visit the garden"},{"time":638052,"text":"is to uproot this plant because it's dead."},{"time":640776,"text":"But if you water it, this is what you get."},{"time":645578,"text":"Absolutely amazing."},{"time":647754,"text":"Now, if you look at our aging process,"},{"time":650250,"text":"the aging process is in fact the loss of water"},{"time":652700,"text":"from the upper epidermis, resulting in wrinkling"},{"time":655874,"text":"as we know it, especially women,"},{"time":657441,"text":"we are so conscious of this."},{"time":659282,"text":"And this plant, in fact, is giving \nthe cosmetic chemists"},{"time":663963,"text":"very important ingredients"},{"time":665953,"text":"that are actually finding ways"},{"time":668720,"text":"to slow down the aging process"},{"time":671110,"text":"and at the same time reinforce the cells"},{"time":673490,"text":"against the onslaught of environmental toxins."}]},{"cues":[{"time":677777,"text":"Now, these four examples"},{"time":680414,"text":"I have just given you"},{"time":683321,"text":"are just a very tiny reminder"},{"time":686755,"text":"as to how our health"},{"time":690492,"text":"and our survival are closely linked"},{"time":693996,"text":"to the health and the resilience"},{"time":696808,"text":"of our ecosystem,"},{"time":698653,"text":"and why we should be very careful"},{"time":700587,"text":"about preserving biodiversity."},{"time":703288,"text":"Every time a forest is cut down,"},{"time":706490,"text":"every time a marsh is filled in,"},{"time":710110,"text":"it is a potential lab that goes with it,"},{"time":713860,"text":"and which we will never, ever recover."},{"time":716168,"text":"And I know what I'm talking about,"},{"time":717735,"text":"coming from Mauritius and missing the dodo."}]},{"cues":[{"time":721067,"text":"Let me finish with just one last example."},{"time":725425,"text":"Conservation issues are normally guided"},{"time":729240,"text":"towards rare, endemic plants,"},{"time":732208,"text":"but what we call exotic plants,"},{"time":734750,"text":"that is, the ones which grow in many\ndifferent habitats across the world,"},{"time":738227,"text":"they also need to be considered."},{"time":740633,"text":"You know why? Because the environment plays"},{"time":743772,"text":"a very important role"},{"time":745527,"text":"in modifying the composition of that plant."}]},{"cues":[{"time":748186,"text":"So let's take a look at this plant here,"},{"time":750817,"text":"Centella asiatica. It's a weed."},{"time":753300,"text":"We call it a weed."},{"time":755448,"text":"Now, Centella asiatica \ngrows across the world"},{"time":758324,"text":"in many different habitats — \nin Africa, in Asia —"},{"time":761106,"text":"and this plant has been instrumental"},{"time":763125,"text":"in providing a solution \nto that dreadful disease"},{"time":765892,"text":"called leprosy in Madagascar in the 1940s."},{"time":770338,"text":"Now, while Centella \ngrows across the world —"},{"time":773868,"text":"in Africa, in Asia — \nthe best quality Centella"},{"time":777159,"text":"comes from Madagascar,"},{"time":779503,"text":"because that Centella contains\nthe three vital ingredients"},{"time":783688,"text":"which are sought after by the pharma"},{"time":785914,"text":"and the cosmetic companies."},{"time":788548,"text":"And the cosmetic companies \nare already using it"},{"time":790797,"text":"to make regenerating cream."}]},{"cues":[{"time":793879,"text":"Now, there is an ancient saying"},{"time":796668,"text":"that for every disease known to mankind,"},{"time":800212,"text":"there is a plant to cure it."},{"time":802394,"text":"Now, you may not \nbelieve in ancient sayings."},{"time":804622,"text":"You may think they're obsolete"},{"time":806185,"text":"now that our science and \ntechnology are so powerful."},{"time":809133,"text":"So you may look on Centella as being"},{"time":811169,"text":"an insignificant, humble weed,"},{"time":814374,"text":"which, if destroyed, won't be missed."},{"time":817700,"text":"But you know, there is no such thing as a weed."},{"time":820135,"text":"It's a plant."},{"time":821889,"text":"It's a living biological lab"},{"time":824768,"text":"that may well have answers"},{"time":826669,"text":"to the question that we may have,"},{"time":828627,"text":"but we have to ensure"},{"time":830517,"text":"that it has the right to live."}]},{"cues":[{"time":833250,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":835128,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}